General.Name: Saga Furs Oyj C
General.Description: Saga Furs Oyj operates an auction house furs in Finland. The company offers finnraccoon, fox, and mink furs. It serves fur breeders and suppliers, clothing manufacturers, and fashion houses. The company was formerly known as Turkistuottajat Oyj and changed its name to Saga Furs Oyj in October 2011. The company was incorporated in 1938 and is based in Vantaa, Finland.
